<item>
            <title>[SLING-8573] ACLs are missing from the converted content packages for regular users and groups</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SLING-8573</link>
                <project id="12310710" key="SLING">Sling</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ACLs are missing from the converted content packages for regular users and groups.&lt;br/&gt;
All &quot;_rep_policy&quot; nodes are removed by the converter from the resulting content package and in the repoinit section of the JSON output there are only the ACLs for service users.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add the ACLs in the repo init for all users, groups, system users, or&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Don&apos;t remove the &quot;_rep_policy&quot; nodes from the resulting content package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
